{"tid":576366,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搭訕美眉不成偷襲臀　水泥工下場慘「判刑3月+罰9萬」","createTime":"2018-02-28T23:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T06:16:55.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8890595396d0cfe05191f69e0ddb399523a30140","tid":576366,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T23:55:52.000Z","msg":"新竹一名33歲楊姓男子從事水泥工，覬覦超商女工讀生美貌，一直搭訕要電話和LINE，但都被拒絕。楊男不死心，竟趁女子忙碌偷摸屁股，她忍無可忍報警，新竹地院依性騷擾防治法判刑3月，易科罰金9萬元。<br />\n<br />\n根據判決書指出，去年7月，楊男到新竹縣新豐鄉一家超商，看見18歲小美身材好，長得又漂亮，多次上前搭訕要電話和LINE都沒成功。小美不予理會，轉身幫其他消費者點飲料，未料將飲料送至用餐區時，楊男竟偷摸她屁股，小美不甘受辱，當場報警。<br />\n<br />\n法官指出，楊男為滿足一己私慾，無視兩性平權與對女性的尊重，趁被害人轉身不及抗拒之際襲臀，顯然不尊重他人身體自主權，進而造成被害人心理陰影，依故意性騷擾少女罪判刑3月，易科罰金則為9萬元。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/12/06/1165499-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2F1165499-XXL.jpg&h=92da675f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲示意圖／資料照<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=352719\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D352719&d=KAJfYNLaML4WSuj7codgJIM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=a316dd66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D352719&h=7023e1e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=352719</a>"},{"pid":"4adf0895aacc06b21eafe5b0eb4067703f14b87f","tid":576366,"uid":81598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:06:04.000Z","msg":"示意圖好似av cut出黎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6eb45aa5ed14efcdb409e1dd40f645a4cc6ea91","tid":576366,"uid":17550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:12:18.000Z","msg":"睇錯偷腎"},{"pid":"bd4ae6487bc1fa893da996ca185965c1cb08f31b","tid":576366,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:14:21.000Z","msg":"台灣罰咁重<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\